import React, {Fragment} from 'react'
import { MDBContainer, MDBCard, MDBCardBody, MDBCardHeader, MDBCardTitle, MDBCardText } from 'mdbreact'

export default function SearchPage() {
    return (
        <MDBContainer>
            <MDBCard className="mt-5">
            <MDBCardHeader className="text-center">Modals</MDBCardHeader>
            <MDBCardBody>
                <MDBCardText>
                    Some quick example text to build on the card title and make
                    up the bulk of the card's content.
                </MDBCardText>
                </MDBCardBody>
            </MDBCard>
        </MDBContainer>
    )
}
